Class LWSingleMalt

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.maltparser.core.lw.parser.LWSingleMalt
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Configuration, DependencyParserConfig

    public final class LWSingleMalt
extends java.lang.Object
implements DependencyParserConfig
    A lightweight version of org.maltparser.parser.SingleMalt. This class can only perform parsing and is used by the concurrent MaltParser model.
    Author:
    Johan Hall
